Claude Official RTL
===================

Copyright (c) 2026 Menachem Samama

All product code in this repository is original work for this project:

- official-runtime/   macOS injection into Anthropic-signed Claude Desktop
- manager/            menu-bar control panel + adapter inventory
- payload-v2/         layout-only in-page RTL engine (CSS + dir; no text rewrites)
- docs/               product documentation for this repository

This repository does NOT contain, vendor, or build from third-party RTL engine
trees such as engine/, dom/, browser/, desktop/, gui/helper patch pipelines from
other open-source Claude RTL projects.

Historical note (context only, not code in this repo):
Early experiments on the author's machine temporarily used a third-party MIT
engine for prototyping while discovering that copy/re-sign approaches break
Claude Desktop account surfaces. The product path here is a different
architecture (runtime inject into the official app) with an original payload.
